| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1015 — Mass File Rename (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 145bc765-3a41-51f5-9221-72d5275e757c"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
